These are Puzzles for 1x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-1::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: boat, subway, roller, tram, airplane, van
1. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1     |       2        |     3     |      4       |   5   |   6    |
| Transport   | subway | airplane | boat | van | tram | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: november, september, february, january, july, june
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Birthday   | january | november | february | june | july | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-3::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: photography, collecting, baking, magic-tricks, fishing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |   3    |    4     |       5       |       6       |
| Hobby   | collecting | baking | fishing | photography | sudoku | magic-tricks |

