3. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |   4    |     5     |   6   |
| Cigar   | dannemann | vegafina | prince | baccarat | ritmeester | bolivar |

