3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |    3    |    4    |   5    |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | western | time-travel | musical | sports | crime | documentary |

