.:: Puzzle 1x6-Level-1-20::.
There 6 different types of food: apple, blueberry, mango, avocado, onion, strawberry
1. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating mango is on the right of the person eating apple##1
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person eating onion##1
6. the person eating avocado is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4      |      5      |   6   |
| Food   | apple | mango | strawberry | onion | blueberry | avocado |

 